        <item>
            <title>1.8.6</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 18:21:28 +0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>71</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.8.6</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's New in 1.8.6</h2><ul></ul><p><strong>Added</strong></p><ul><li>Undo now restores original Finder tags and comments</li><li>Better placeholders for document, spreadsheet, and presentation files</li></ul><p><strong>Improved</strong></p><ul><li>Cleaner thumbnails in AI Rename, Activity, and queue views</li><li>Smoother Settings and menu bar updates while Zush is working</li><li>More reliable App Store consent flow during setup</li></ul><p><strong>Fixed</strong></p><ul><li>Removed the old AI category field from rename analysis</li><li>Better recovery when Groq returns invalid structured responses</li></ul>
]]></description>
